  Name: Murad, siege laborer
  Icon: {fileID: 1208347981, guid: b2407ce4cf73ad348aec15ba9990f7a1, type: 3}
  Description: "He carried earth and timber, never a weapon. A counter-battery shot
    collapsed a trench wall onto his ribs; his chest caves inward when he breathes.\n\nTreatment:
